1. in "Tables" there is an "apply schema" button.
It directs the browser to /admin/schema/apply
-- Error
   The "path" arguement must be of type string. Received undefined
   [ back to dashboard ]

2. When on the dashboard page. If you click the app that is already selected, it should take you to the tables page.

3. The Data link takes the browser to /admin/data/authors (the first table in the list)
Contents is the same as in /admin/schema/apply

